<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="45540000t" end="58470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">出发了呢…</p>
<p begin="66810000t" end="80990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="85160000t" end="101010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">该怎么说好呢</p>
<p begin="104350000t" end="130210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">我们被丢下来了呢</p>
<p begin="135210000t" end="145220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">确实如此</p>
<p begin="150230000t" end="161490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">自从来到这里之后</p>
<p begin="161490000t" end="189850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">我们完全没有存在的意义呢</p>
<p begin="196520000t" end="217790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">就算我们上了战场</p>
<p begin="221960000t" end="232810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">也什么事都办不到…</p>
<p begin="241150000t" end="254500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">我明明知道的</p>
<p begin="261170000t" end="278270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">但是真不想承认</p>
<p begin="294540000t" end="302880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">可是啊…</p>
<p begin="313310000t" end="341250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">你不会选择放弃对吧</p>
<p begin="361690000t" end="373370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">当然咯</p>
<p begin="380460000t" end="415910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">真是的 要是你肯放弃的话</p>
<p begin="415910000t" end="444690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">我的亚德同学一万人后宫计划</p>
<p begin="444690000t" end="467630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">也能顺利进行了说</p>
<p begin="467630000t" end="489310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">我才不会准你建什么后宫的</p>
<p begin="489310000t" end="511420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">话说回来 人数怎么增加啦</p>
<p begin="545620000t" end="565220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">伊莉娜大人 吉妮大人</p>
<p begin="570650000t" end="589410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">有重大消息要告知两位</p>
<p begin="595250000t" end="606510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">重大…</p>
<p begin="610270000t" end="620700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">消息?</p>
<p begin="626530000t" end="633210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">是的</p>
<p begin="638210000t" end="658650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">亚德大人下了命令</p>
<p begin="658650000t" end="688260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">要请两位立刻出击</p>
<p begin="708280000t" end="743740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">这表示也有我们办得到的事情 对吧</p>
<p begin="794620000t" end="806300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">拉蒂玛小姐</p>
<p begin="806300000t" end="826730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">可以请你說明一下吗</p>
<p begin="832990000t" end="849260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">我们这次出击</p>
<p begin="851340000t" end="879700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">是亚德大人所想出的作战行动</p>
<p begin="885130000t" end="895550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">亚德大人他</p>
<p begin="895550000t" end="918910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">看穿了"魔王"不死之身的真面目</p>
<p begin="918910000t" end="944350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">他命令我寻找适当的时机</p>
<p begin="944350000t" end="980640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">与两位一同前往魔王所占领的城堡</p>
<p begin="982720000t" end="1010670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">为什么不直接跟我们说</p>
<p begin="1010670000t" end="1019840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">而是告诉拉蒂玛?</p>
<p begin="1022350000t" end="1040280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">因为在神不知鬼不觉之中行动</p>
<p begin="1040280000t" end="1051960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">是最为重要的</p>
<p begin="1092000000t" end="1099920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">那么</p>
<p begin="1099920000t" end="1124120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">先告诉我们作战计划的内容吧</p>
<p begin="1127450000t" end="1153310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">亚德大人推测 魔王的不死之身</p>
<p begin="1153310000t" end="1188760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">是使用了分离灵体的秘术</p>
<p begin="1191680000t" end="1217960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">分离灵体的秘术…</p>
<p begin="1217960000t" end="1230470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">就是那个对吧</p>
<p begin="1234640000t" end="1259670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">将灵魂与肉体分开的…</p>
<p begin="1265510000t" end="1290940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">然后封入适合的媒介之中</p>
<p begin="1300530000t" end="1308050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">所谓的死亡</p>
<p begin="1308050000t" end="1335580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">指的是同时失去灵魂与肉体</p>
<p begin="1341000000t" end="1361020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">所以只要将两者分离开来</p>
<p begin="1361020000t" end="1375620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">基本上就能成为不死之身</p>
<p begin="1397720000t" end="1407730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">然后呢</p>
<p begin="1411490000t" end="1427330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">根据亚德大人的说法</p>
<p begin="1427330000t" end="1454450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">这个术式有两个缺点</p>
<p begin="1460700000t" end="1481140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">第一个 是媒介与施术者</p>
<p begin="1481140000t" end="1504500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">不能离开一定距离以上</p>
<p begin="1510330000t" end="1533690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">另一点 只要破坏媒介</p>
<p begin="1538280000t" end="1554960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">就会失去不死之身</p>
<p begin="1562800000t" end="1604600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">魔王应该将媒介连同 灵体移动至占领的城堡中了</p>
<p begin="1607510000t" end="1623360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">亚德大人是这么推测的</p>
<p begin="1623360000t" end="1636290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">这么说来</p>
<p begin="1636290000t" end="1656730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">瓦尔瓦德斯大人在会议中</p>
<p begin="1656730000t" end="1688010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">也说了只要抵达城池就可以获胜呢</p>
<p begin="1693430000t" end="1735560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">我们的机密任务就是破坏这个媒介?</p>
<p begin="1743480000t" end="1758500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">正是如此</p>
<p begin="1769340000t" end="1776850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">如今</p>
<p begin="1776850000t" end="1806460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">在瓦尔瓦德斯大人指挥之下进行的战斗</p>
<p begin="1809800000t" end="1836490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">不过只是佯攻作战</p>
<p begin="1844840000t" end="1867770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">恐怕无人知晓这个事实</p>
<p begin="1879040000t" end="1912820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">亚德大人发现了通往城堡的密道</p>
<p begin="1916990000t" end="1927420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">只要使用那条密道…</p>
<p begin="1931590000t" end="1939930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">可是…</p>
<p begin="1939930000t" end="1954950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">为什么是我们</p>
<p begin="1962040000t" end="1984140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">如此重责大任 为什么…</p>
<p begin="2014170000t" end="2041700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">这还真不像你耶 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="2052130000t" end="2067560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">还以为你在这种时候</p>
<p begin="2067560000t" end="2096340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">反倒会感到开心的</p>
<p begin="2108010000t" end="2139300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">要是知道了伊莉娜小姐是这么没用的人</p>
<p begin="2144300000t" end="2171830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">亚德同学一定会很失望吧</p>
<p begin="2173910000t" end="2179340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">什…</p>
<p begin="2184760000t" end="2209370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">你 你少说蠢话了</p>
<p begin="2209370000t" end="2232310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">他才不可能会失望呢</p>
<p begin="2242320000t" end="2251910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">对对</p>
<p begin="2259000000t" end="2288610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">这种态度最适合你了</p>
<p begin="2297370000t" end="2333240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">这种时候 只要"好耶!""万岁!"这样</p>
<p begin="2339910000t" end="2365360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">没神经的大呼小叫就好了</p>
<p begin="2376620000t" end="2402480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">对啊! 就是这样!</p>
<p begin="2407480000t" end="2419160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">看我们的吧</p>
<p begin="2460870000t" end="2468790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">趴下</p>
<p begin="2518420000t" end="2528020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">拉蒂玛</p>
<p begin="2545950000t" end="2558050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">两位快走吧</p>
<p begin="2560970000t" end="2579320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">由我来挡下敌人</p>
<p begin="2584730000t" end="2600590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">快! 快点走!</p>
<p begin="2616440000t" end="2627280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">知道了</p>
<p begin="3008500000t" end="3029350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">就这样一口气镇压对方</p>
<p begin="3099000000t" end="3133210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">受不了 莉迪姐姐到底上哪去了</p>
<p begin="3135710000t" end="3152390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">到底什么时候才会回来</p>
<p begin="3152390000t" end="3172410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">真希望她可以说一声</p>
<p begin="3254990000t" end="3267510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">那 那个是…</p>
<p begin="3272510000t" end="3286280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">没有错</p>
<p begin="3286280000t" end="3310470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">就是封有魔王灵体的媒介</p>
<p begin="3347170000t" end="3363020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">要上咯 吉妮</p>
<p begin="3365100000t" end="3371780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">好的</p>
<p begin="3509410000t" end="3522760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">可恶…</p>
<p begin="3524850000t" end="3544870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">什么 怎么回事</p>
<p begin="3551120000t" end="3561130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">没有用的</p>
<p begin="3577820000t" end="3594500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">因为这种拘束魔法</p>
<p begin="3597000000t" end="3619520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">具有封住魔力的效果</p>
<p begin="3626200000t" end="3638290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">为什么…</p>
<p begin="3644970000t" end="3668740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">这是…怎么一回事…</p>
<p begin="3687930000t" end="3698770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">拉蒂玛</p>
<p begin="3744650000t" end="3763840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">伊莉娜小姐 吉妮同学</p>
<p begin="3773010000t" end="3793030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">真是令人怀念的面孔</p>
<p begin="3800540000t" end="3837240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">本以为再也见不到她们了…</p>
<p begin="3848500000t" end="3877280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">我就特意说出这套无趣的说词吧</p>
<p begin="3877280000t" end="3895220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">如果想要人质的小命</p>
<p begin="3895220000t" end="3913150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">就加入我军</p>
<p begin="3923160000t" end="3939430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">若我说不的话</p>
<p begin="3939430000t" end="3954030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">那两人会怎么样</p>
<p begin="3959450000t" end="3975300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">不会怎么样</p>
<p begin="3978220000t" end="3990730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">我说过了吧</p>
<p begin="3990730000t" end="4012420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">这不过是一出闹剧</p>
<p begin="4027850000t" end="4058300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">你并无加害于她们的打算是吗…</p>
<p begin="4070810000t" end="4103760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">你是打算帮我找借口吗</p>
<p begin="4103760000t" end="4122940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">为了拯救人质</p>
<p begin="4122940000t" end="4146720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">与你联手也是不得已的</p>
<p begin="4155480000t" end="4177170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">你的想法 我都看穿了</p>
<p begin="4181340000t" end="4202610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">莉迪亚的心意也是</p>
<p begin="4206780000t" end="4223460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">那家伙临死之际</p>
<p begin="4223460000t" end="4242650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">肯定没有任何遗憾或后悔</p>
<p begin="4242650000t" end="4261420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">相当满足吧</p>
<p begin="4271430000t" end="4281020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">可是…</p>
<p begin="4281020000t" end="4301040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">我们的感受又怎么样呢</p>
<p begin="4301040000t" end="4323140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">自己亲手杀死了挚友</p>
<p begin="4323140000t" end="4354840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">用自己的双手促成了这样的结果</p>
<p begin="4358180000t" end="4383620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">要永远背负这个罪行…</p>
<p begin="4391130000t" end="4421990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">即使莉迪亚自己期望凄惨的结局</p>
<p begin="4424500000t" end="4448690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">还是希望她可以得到幸福</p>
<p begin="4448690000t" end="4474960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">这不是理所当然的愿望吗</p>
<p begin="4479550000t" end="4499990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">若要让莉迪亚活下去</p>
<p begin="4499990000t" end="4524180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">我需要夺走众多生命</p>
<p begin="4528350000t" end="4561300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">会把这世界逼迫到毁灭的边缘吧</p>
<p begin="4567560000t" end="4593410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">可是 只要这样可以拯救莉迪亚</p>
<p begin="4593410000t" end="4607600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">就太划算了</p>
<p begin="4612180000t" end="4634710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">我已经感觉不到人们的性命</p>
<p begin="4634710000t" end="4658060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">有何可贵之处</p>
<p begin="4662650000t" end="4676410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">你也是</p>
<p begin="4676410000t" end="4707280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">内心深处也怀有一样的想法吧</p>
<p begin="4711870000t" end="4733550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">那么就没有必要犹豫</p>
<p begin="4779430000t" end="4803620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">既然你还在继续犹豫</p>
<p begin="4803620000t" end="4825730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">就再给你一个借口吧</p>
