<p begin="9518330000t" end="9547950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">不该说出那种话的…</p>
<p begin="9552540000t" end="9576310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">没有打算说出口的</p>
<p begin="9580900000t" end="9590490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">我…</p>
<p begin="9590490000t" end="9612180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">应该把不希望你死去的感情</p>
<p begin="9612180000t" end="9663060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">坦率地将真心话表达出来</p>
<p begin="9669740000t" end="9691420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">那样的结局…</p>
<p begin="9691420000t" end="9717280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">莉迪亚迎来那么凄惨的下场</p>
<p begin="9717280000t" end="9735220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">我绝不承认</p>
<p begin="9737720000t" end="9746900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">因此</p>
<p begin="9746900000t" end="9764000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">我要拯救莉迪亚</p>
<p begin="9764000000t" end="9794030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">自愿让莉迪亚来制裁我</p>
<p begin="9794030000t" end="9828640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">莉迪亚应该要享受幸福才对</p>
<p begin="10111430000t" end="10121850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">这样啊…</p>
<p begin="10135620000t" end="10161060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">如果这是你自己的意思的话…</p>
<p begin="10207770000t" end="10217370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">结束了</p>
<p begin="10217370000t" end="10231130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">迪萨斯特·罗格(彻底失败的寇匪)</p>
<p begin="10231130000t" end="10246140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">我的分身</p>
<p begin="10257820000t" end="10270750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">你这家伙…</p>
<p begin="10270750000t" end="10307870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">真的认为…这样好吗…</p>
<p begin="10320800000t" end="10336230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">给我想起来…</p>
<p begin="10339990000t" end="10358760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">跟莉迪亚在一起的日子…</p>
<p begin="10360420000t" end="10396290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">那是多么的…宝贵…</p>
<p begin="10525590000t" end="10536430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">拜托…</p>
<p begin="10540610000t" end="10550620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">求你了…</p>
<p begin="10558540000t" end="10575640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">我不能失败…</p>
<p begin="10583150000t" end="10600250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">这次绝对不能…</p>
<p begin="10608170000t" end="10634030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">直到失去后才真正理解到…</p>
<p begin="10639450000t" end="10658640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">我对莉迪亚的心意…</p>
<p begin="10666150000t" end="10693680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">所以才想要…拯救她…</p>
<p begin="10701600000t" end="10734550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">我…爱着…她…</p>
<p begin="10805040000t" end="10817130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">你…</p>
<p begin="10823810000t" end="10848000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">再次犯下了罪行…</p>
<p begin="10848000000t" end="10858010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">不要忘了</p>
<p begin="10867600000t" end="10889700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">你再次…</p>
<p begin="10889700000t" end="10915150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">再次亲手…</p>
<p begin="10915150000t" end="10942670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">杀了莉迪亚…</p>
<p begin="11042360000t" end="11052780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">这是…?</p>
<p begin="11084900000t" end="11106170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">看样子是要回去了吧</p>
<p begin="11112840000t" end="11121190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">也好</p>
<p begin="11121190000t" end="11143710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">对你们来说这样是最好的吧</p>
<p begin="11148710000t" end="11160390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">莉迪亚大人</p>
<p begin="11160390000t" end="11181660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">您知道我们的来历吗</p>
<p begin="11195840000t" end="11208770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">隐隐约约啦</p>
<p begin="11387280000t" end="11421490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">可以让我问一个问题吗</p>
<p begin="11428990000t" end="11443170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">未来变得怎么样了</p>
<p begin="11453180000t" end="11501570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">有成为大家都能笑着生活的世界吗</p>
<p begin="11546190000t" end="11557450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">未来…</p>
<p begin="11562460000t" end="11589150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">未来成了如同莉迪亚大人期望般的</p>
<p begin="11589150000t" end="11612510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">美好世界</p>
<p begin="11621690000t" end="11641290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">每天都尽是些开心的事</p>
<p begin="11641290000t" end="11658390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">虽然偶尔会吵吵架</p>
<p begin="11661730000t" end="11677160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">不过大家都很幸福哦</p>
<p begin="11684250000t" end="11722200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">我觉得已经成了个大家都能欢笑的世界</p>
<p begin="11732210000t" end="11742220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">这样啊…</p>
<p begin="11748480000t" end="11776420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">我们的牺牲并没有白费…</p>
<p begin="11784350000t" end="11816460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">最后可以请你们捎个口信吗</p>
<p begin="11821890000t" end="11854840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">有件事我非得告诉亚德不可…</p>
<p begin="12025010000t" end="12040440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">这是怎么了…</p>
<p begin="12047110000t" end="12056290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">报告</p>
<p begin="12066300000t" end="12085480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">魔王军开始败退了</p>
<p begin="12089650000t" end="12100080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">真的吗</p>
<p begin="12128020000t" end="12142620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">莫非是他们…</p>
<p begin="12165150000t" end="12175160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">快</p>
<p begin="12175160000t" end="12194760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">一只都不要放过</p>
<p begin="12208520000t" end="12227710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">各位 肃静</p>
<p begin="12237300000t" end="12254820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">我军已经胜利</p>
<p begin="12257320000t" end="12281090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">不需要再追杀</p>
<p begin="12349080000t" end="12372850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">太好啦</p>
<p begin="12382450000t" end="12393710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">辛苦啦</p>
<p begin="12420820000t" end="12440420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">我什么事情都没有做</p>
<p begin="12449600000t" end="12473370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">除了拥有优秀的部下以外</p>
<p begin="12482960000t" end="12499650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">亚德·梅堤欧尔怎么了呢</p>
<p begin="12502570000t" end="12515080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">他没跟你在一起吗</p>
<p begin="12547610000t" end="12558040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">他回去了</p>
<p begin="12568460000t" end="12583900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">回到属于自己的地方了</p>
<p begin="12601000000t" end="12612260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">这样啊</p>
<p begin="12641040000t" end="12653970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">结束了呢</p>
<p begin="12667310000t" end="12676490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">不…</p>
<p begin="12685670000t" end="12697760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">现在才要开始</p>
<p begin="12756570000t" end="12782850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">对于漂亮完成任务的你们</p>
<p begin="12782850000t" end="12808290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">我不禁百感交集…</p>
<p begin="12815380000t" end="12834560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">你们究竟是何方神圣</p>
<p begin="12838320000t" end="12857090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">到底有什么目的</p>
<p begin="12857090000t" end="12872520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">可以告诉我吗</p>
<p begin="12877520000t" end="12905050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">并没有可以表达出我们的话语…</p>
<p begin="12911310000t" end="12935500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">可是 只有一点要请你相信</p>
<p begin="12940920000t" end="12973870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">至少我是站在你们这边的</p>
<p begin="12979290000t" end="12990550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">即便如此</p>
<p begin="12990550000t" end="13032260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">我仍期望从此再也不要见到你</p>
<p begin="13036850000t" end="13061040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">我也跟你一样…</p>
<p begin="13095660000t" end="13107340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">梅堤欧尔…</p>
<p begin="13107340000t" end="13123190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">亚德·梅堤欧尔</p>
<p begin="13123190000t" end="13139450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">到了 快醒醒</p>
<p begin="13146540000t" end="13169900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">叫你快醒醒啦</p>
<p begin="13191590000t" end="13205350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">真是的 受不了</p>
<p begin="13208690000t" end="13234550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">你们三个都睡得太熟了吧</p>
<p begin="13286680000t" end="13300450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">快点下车</p>
<p begin="13306290000t" end="13335900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">其他学生都已经开始移动了</p>
<p begin="13361340000t" end="13379690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">好怀念哦</p>
<p begin="13379690000t" end="13401380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">过去的王都金士格瑞弗</p>
<p begin="13405550000t" end="13426820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">这里没什么变化呢</p>
<p begin="13436830000t" end="13454350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">虽然发生了很多事…</p>
<p begin="13458100000t" end="13475620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">终于回来了呢</p>
<p begin="13480210000t" end="13494390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">对了 亚德</p>
<p begin="13498560000t" end="13528590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">临别的时候莉迪亚大人托了我们口信</p>
<p begin="13536930000t" end="13550700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">口信吗</p>
<p begin="13561960000t" end="13571130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">她说啊…</p>
<p begin="13581560000t" end="13594070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">无论如何</p>
<p begin="13599910000t" end="13614510000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">不管发生什么事</p>
<p begin="13627020000t" end="13649960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">我们都是挚友</p>
<p begin="13676660000t" end="13693340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="13696260000t" end="13714190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">你在做什么呢</p>
<p begin="13717950000t" end="13730460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">现在就过去</p>
<p begin="13742550000t" end="13815130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">"冲动 渴望 Starting over"</p>
<p begin="13820550000t" end="13866850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">"既然选择了重生 就不能畏惧"</p>
<p begin="13866850000t" end="13910220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">"向天真的过去 道声再会"</p>
<p begin="13912720000t" end="13960270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">"在雾灰朦胧的 这个世界"</p>
<p begin="13960270000t" end="13991970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">"只会随波逐流过活"</p>
<p begin="13991970000t" end="14047030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">"便掌握不到的自由 以此为目标吧"</p>
<p begin="14049940000t" end="14068300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">"比起孤单地变强"</p>
<p begin="14068300000t" end="14093740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">莉迪亚 谢谢你</p>
<p begin="14093740000t" end="14118760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">"更想要互相分享的温暖"</p>
<p begin="14118760000t" end="14152960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">"找到了那道光"</p>
<p begin="14152960000t" end="14192590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">"去轻轻地拥抱吧"</p>
</div>
